sful artists there are, the less power middlemen have.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D=
"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Ov=
er the next 100 minutes, Spotify dropped subtle clues about the labels&#821=
7; diminishing power. Today, Spotify is the unquestioned audio aggregator, =
which allows it to do all of the things that labels can do, at scale, more =
cheaply.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Recall what a label does: A&amp;R Support and Fu=
